  "texts": [
    "In iterating, we systematically screened the 1398 titles and abstracts of papers deemed eligible for the study.",
    "Three people were included at this stage to reduce biases that could result from a single screener.",
    "Following this, all four members of the article screening and selection team conducted a manual full-text screening of the remaining 382 articles against the inclusion criteria in Table 2.",
    "Finally, the two authors (TAB, AB) involved in the article screening and selection team and one of the internal reviewers performed the final extraction that led to the 45 included articles.",
    "During the last stage of this process, meetings were held between the four authors (TAB, AB, ES, MK; the latter two of which have a background in organisational psychology and human factors, respectively) to discuss the articles excluded and selected."
  ],
